Package GSILabs.BModel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Event
    An event is any happening for which a ticket can be purchased.
    ImpermanentEvent
    An impermanent event is an event that has a limited time span, typically restricted to minutes or hours.
    LastingEvent
    Event that spans over several dates and/or locations.
    Performer
    A performer is any kind of person or group of person in charge of an event for which a ticket can be purchased.
